title: Auburn dismisses senior wide receiver D’haquille Williams
text:
Auburn dismisses senior wide receiver D’haquille Williams Tools By Alabama News Network 
Story Created: Oct 5, 2015 at 9:15 PM CDT AUBURN, Ala.—Auburn senior wide receiver D’haquille Williams has been dismissed from the football team, head coach Gus Malzahn announced Monday.“When individuals fail to meet the expectations of our program, there has to be consequences,” Malzahn said. “I gave D’haquille the chance to prove himself. I am disappointed that it did not work out.”
